        Zapo캜ni u캜enje?
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-200 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Zapo캜ni svoj put u bakteriologiji danas. Svako poglavlje je samostalna cjelina
        s teorijom, prakti캜nim vje쬭ama i provjerom znanja.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
        <a
          href="/sadrzaj/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-purple-700 font-bold rounded-full shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105 no-underline text-lg"
        >
          <span>Sadr쬬j</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 ml-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
